org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.helpers

Class AbstractTermedStatementDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.helpers.AbstractTermedStatementDocument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityDocument, StatementDocument, TermedDocument
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    JacksonTermedStatementDocument, TermedStatementDocumentImpl

    public abstract class AbstractTermedStatementDocument
extends Object
implements TermedDocument, StatementDocument
    Abstract base class for implementations of TermedDocument and StatementDocument. It does not store any data, but it implements the required find methods that access the data. Specific implementations can overwrite some find methods with more efficient solutions based on internal data structures.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch
